## Scope

This report records a deterministic parameter override applied to a
finished ClawModeler run. The new run's inputs, accessibility,
VMT-screening, and transit-metrics artifacts are recomputed from the
same staged inputs under `workspace/inputs/` as the base run;
`project_scores.csv` reflects the override's scoring weights and row
filters. No LLM is called and no narrative is generated — the grounding
covenant is preserved. Every change is mirrored as a
`what_if_scenario` or `what_if_project_delta` fact_block in the new
run's `fact_blocks.jsonl`.

